Interface InteractProtocol

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SuperTanker

    public interface InteractProtocol

    MULTI-AGENT SYSTEM : A Communication interface that can be used between tankers.

    This allows tankers to share knowledge between each other for necessary needs such as avoiding conflicting tasks and sharing tanker locations.

    The interface contains the OpenSystem, A distributive multi-agent system that shares tasks among any agents that are in it. A tanker is free to join or leave the OpenSystem anytime it wants.

    For more information, see OpenSystem
